text: Teredidae is a family of beetles in the order Coleoptera, formerly included within the family Bothrideridae. ==Genera== * Anommatus Wesmael, 1835 * Oxylaemus Erichson, 1845 * Rustleria Stephan, 1989 * Sosylopsis Grouvelle, 1910 * Sysolus Grouvelle, 1908 * Teredolaemus Sharp, 1885 * Teredomorphus Heinze, 1943 * Teredus Dejean, 1835 * Xylariophilus Pal & Lawrence, 1986 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * * * Category:Coccinelloidea Category:Polyphaga families
title: Teredidae
